"\t| 123456\t|\t       +----------------+\n"
"\t| 7890\t\t|\n"
"\t|\t\t|\t       +----------------+\n"
"\t| example\t|  CTRL-D -->  | 7890\t\t|\n"
"\t+---------------+\t       |\t\t|\n"
"\t\t\t\t       | example\t|\n"
